title: Public lecture: 25th anniversary of St.Gallen-Liberec (University of St Gallen)
text: ( Source : University of St Gallen ) The St.Gallen-Liberec cooperation has been in existence for 25 years. This partnership between the two regions will be celebrated with a varied anniversary programme, including a six-part public lecture
